				\begin{document}$$\mathbf{A}\mathbf{U}\mathbf{C} (\text{mgh}/\text{dl})=\frac{{\varvec{P}}{\varvec{G}}\left(0\right)+PG\left(30\right)*2+PG\left(60\right)*3+PG\left(120\right)*2}{4}$$\end{document}AUC(mgh/dl)=PG0+PG30∗2+PG60∗3+PG120∗24
